2008-12-15  Andreas Kupries  <andreask@activestate.com>

	* cmpWrite.c: Handle TIP#336 addition of API to access
	interp->errorLine.

2007-06-21  Andreas Kupries  <andreask@activestate.com>

	* cmpWrite.c (CreateInstLocList): Tcl 8.5 specific change.
	  Compensate for the INST_START_CMD the 8.5 core compiler may emit
	  before calling our LocalProcCompileProc. Not doing so leaves us
	  with an incorrect offset to the 'proc' bytecode sequence,
	  causing us to bytecompile only those procedures specified as the
	  very first command of a script, and none else.

2007-03-19  Andreas Kupries <andreask@activestate.com>

	* cmpWPkg.c: Added command 'getTclVer'. Returns the version of Tcl
	  the package was compiled against. Allows us to check this at
	  runtime against the active Tcl version.

