	* configure.in: Bumped version to 1.6. Regenerated configure.
	* configure:

	* cmpWrite.c: Applied patch by Uwe Traum to handle the 8.5
	  specific JumpTableInfo (compiled 'switch'). Made conditional on
	  the version of Tcl the package is compiled against.

